summary:
Anne Garcia is a 31-year-old software developer working in the technology sector. She is Latino/Hispanic and identifies as a straight woman, using the pronouns she/her. Anne completed her graduate studies at the University of California, Los Angeles and currently lives in LA. She hails from Santa Fe, New Mexico and speaks both English and Spanish. 

Her interests include coding, biking, traveling, and cooking, with values rooted in environmental conservation, social equality, and lifelong learning. Anne is politically liberal, agnostic and is looking for a life partner in a monogamous relationship. She does not currently have children but is open to having them in the future. 

Anne also leads an active lifestyle, drinks socially, doesn't smoke or use marijuana. She owns a pet dog, falls under the Virgo zodiac sign, and identifies as an INTJ personality type.

Her desired partner would be a straight man, within the age range of 30 to 40 years. He should lead an active lifestyle, be open to having children, and prefer not to smoke or use marijuana. Drinking is acceptable to her.
